<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, January 7 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 2,763.47 on Thursday, down 122.51
points, or 4.18 percent, from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was active with the turnover reaching about 109
trillion Turkish Liras (over 342 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 137.56 points, or 3.71 percent,
to close at 3,510.59 points, the industrial index fell 116.08
points, or 5.49 percent, to close at 1,968.10 points and the
services index went down 122.62 points, or 2.48 percent, to
close at 4,134.11 points. 
</P>
