<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, January 8 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 2,721.51 points on Friday, down
41.96 points, or 1.44 percent, from Thursday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was active with the turnover reaching over 84
trillion Turkish Liras (266 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 71.44 points, or 2.00 percent,
to close at 3,439.15 points, the industrial index fell 5.83
points, or 0.19 percent, to close at 1,962.28 points, and the
services index went down 45.98 points, or 0.98 percent, to
close at 4,088.12 points. 
</P>
