province, the minister said that no one has so far been arrested
in connection with the incident of terrorism, and investigations
are still continuing.
</P>
<P>
About 16 Shia worshippers were killed and more than 20 others
wounded Monday during an armed attack by four masked men at
Imambargah near the central Punjab town of Muzaffargarh. 
