<HEADLINE> Explosion Kills Eight Shandong Residents </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JINAN, January 8 (Xinhua) -- A truck carrying fireworks
exploded at a market in Linyi, east China's Shandong Province, on
Thursday, killing eight people and leaving three victims with
serious burns.
</P>
<P>
