earlier at Kuchchaweli were heading for Mullaitivu, the spokesman
said.
</P>
<P>
He said the navy continued with the attack destroying the boats
despite stiff resistance from the rebels of the Liberation Tigers
of Tamil Eelam (LTTE) who have been fighting a 16-year war for a
separate state in Sri Lanka.
</P>
<P>
There were no casualties among the naval troops, he added.
