in 1998 went up 12 percent to 237,473 vehicles from 210,386 in
1997.
</P>
<P>
It said 456,659 vehicles were made last year, compared to
446,306 in 1997.
</P>
<P>
A total of 455,371 vehicles were sold from the 1998
production, compared to sales of 426,338 in 1997.
(Argentina-Car-Production)
</P>
