miles away from Kood island off the Thai Chanthaburi Province, the
newspaper reported.
</P>
<P>
It was believed to be an act of revenge for the murder of three
Cambodian immigration officers on December 24 by fishermen of
unidentified nationalities, said the report.
</P>
<P>
