</P>
<P>
The attack was reported to the Thai Navy's First Fleet, which
dispatched officials to hunt for the Cambodians.
</P>
<P>
During the hunt, the officials managed to rescue 15 Thai
crewmen on board one of the seized vessels.
</P>
<P>
The Cambodians escaped with the three hostages.
</P>
<P>
The Thai authorities are currently trying to seek the release
of the hostages through diplomatic channels. 
