when Croatia's Tamara Boros defeated Germany's Jing Tian-Zorner
21-18, 18-21, 18-21, 21-17, 21-14.
</P>
<P>
Boros now meets China's Lin Ling, who ousted Germany's
Qianghong Gotsch 21-12, 21-17, 20-22, 21-18.
</P>
<P>
The other six winners for China were Sun Jin, Li Ju, Wang Hui,
Wang Nan, Yang Ying and Zang Yining. 
