The enterprises focus on the areas of bio-engineering, light
industry, foodstuffs, environmental protection, and
pharmaceuticals and are exploring overseas markets.
</P>
<P>
A number of them have become strong through merger and
cooperation and made a name in the nation through outstanding
performance. 
