Wednesday he would not call such a meeting until he got guidelines
from the Security Council.
</P>
<P>
According to UNSCOM officials, no specific date has been set
for the meeting and it may happen at the end of this month.
</P>
<P>
The 23-member board meets about twice a year on the work of the
UNSCOM. 
